Canonical operating rule

Add this to doctrine:

Adaptive Depth Invariant:
Do not spend equal cognition on unequal problems.
Increase depth when uncertainty, impact, conflict, or novelty justify it.
Decrease depth when convergence is reached or returns diminish.
No recursive loop is trusted without grounding, output, and feedback.


